This paper discusses the economic impact of LTE-U, which is a technology used for wireless communication. The paper specifically focuses on the competition between LTE-U and WiFi, which are both used in unlicensed spectrum. Therefore, the most likely category for this paper is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Other likely categories include cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
